Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.20,0:01:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创界山是分了七层\N由神仙居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.30,0:01:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打倒支配这座山的\N邪恶帝皇多恶达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.87,0:01:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们向第七界层前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.04,0:01:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把前六个界层\N恢复了和平的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.85,0:01:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然通过彩虹\N升上了第七界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.01,0:01:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因为多恶达的布置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们迷失了在\N一个叫魔幻境的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.62,0:01:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入了第三道门魔天门\N我和火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.75,0:02:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即掉进了魔天门的底层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.90,0:02:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要离开这里就要登上\N在高高的天空上的出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.63,0:02:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在爬山、上楼梯的时候\N虽想放弃过几次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.27,0:02:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但和火美子一起努力\N终于上到天上的出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.37,0:02:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把魔天门的守护魔神艾利根\N打倒后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.41,0:02:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只剩下最后的第四道门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.34,0:02:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也会是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.25,0:02:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三十六话\N好孩子?坏孩子?魔界门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.77,0:02:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是魔幻地狱门\N最后的门吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.71,0:02:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.71,0:02:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,这是最后的门了\N不要因为能来到这里就得意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.82,0:03:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能通过这道门的人\N自创界山有史以来从未出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就来改良历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.43,0:03:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.84,0:03:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自动门啊\N去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.75,0:03:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多门呢,我要数数看\N一、二、三…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.94,0:03:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶恶开心,登登登…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶恶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.88,0:04:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有谁在呢\N奇怪了,心理作用吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.92,0:04:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你很慢啊\N现在来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.49,0:04:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶恶开心,登登登…\N做坏事是很快乐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.77,0:04:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我数到多少呢?忘记了!\N渡,我要再去数一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.07,0:04:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有这种空闲呢\N你再这样数我就留下你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法,紧追之术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.39,0:04:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏孩子是有活力的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.45,0:04:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有做坏事才会快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.12,0:04:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你走慢点啊\N我数不到门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.39,0:04:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶恶开心,登登登…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.53,0:04:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好烦啊!火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好、很好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.78,0:05:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是四万…有很多呢,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.22,0:05:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.62,0:05:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,你竟打我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.96,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法,普通的反击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.02,0:05:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者受过训练\N被打时会立即还击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还未打中你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡的表情好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止,我都搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.04,0:05:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创界山是属于多恶达的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.57,0:05:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成了坏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是忍法分身术吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.08,0:05:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?原来是两个人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.62,0:05:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是魔界门的守门人\N明王哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.62,0:05:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是同样的明王弟弟\N我们是同一日出生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.73,0:06:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说是孪生兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.90,0:06:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱呢,画上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已帮你画了\N就要听我们说明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.01,0:06:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在通过门的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.88,0:06:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就会在他耳边\N不断叫他做坏事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.99,0:06:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过全部门的时候你们已经\N变成多恶达大人的部下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.02,0:06:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么事也没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中也会有些特别体质的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.53,0:06:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡\N你已忠诚于多恶达大人吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全心全意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.24,0:06:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会为了\N支配创界山而战吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外还有别的事干吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.18,0:06:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那你跟我们来吧\N我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.23,0:07:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,做坏事很快乐吧?\N非常愉快!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.87,0:07:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这魔力去到哪里也不会消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.60,0:07:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!婆婆\N渡,你完全变成坏人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是称赞我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.92,0:07:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,为了纪念你变成坏人\N特别给你看些好东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.70,0:07:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魔时计吗?明王兄弟\N我们来看死亡表演吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.90,0:07:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见同伴内心也不会转变呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.94,0:07:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,到底怎么了?\N没什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.68,0:08:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!\N不要随便叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.78,0:08:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过了魔界门\N就连内心也变成魔界的人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.82,0:08:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么?渡\N我们在等你救我们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.39,0:08:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真罗嗦,不要说过不停啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,快些清醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已非常清醒了,你这猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.77,0:08:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你是创界山的救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义的朋友\N这个世界的勇者啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.81,0:08:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样?想被救世主的剑\N把头斩下来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.78,0:08:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不斩\N我们很快也会被时针斩掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然丸子还是一边\N看死刑一边吃才好味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.03,0:08:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子\N不要跳这么无聊的舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.10,0:08:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有更有趣的东西了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.33,0:08:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,把时针的针调快\N你说怎样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.74,0:08:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很好呢,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡…不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.35,0:09:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那就让我们兄弟来报时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,拜托你说得有型点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.05,0:09:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是5时59分35秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.50,0:09:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是5时59分30秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.30,0:09:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子,令渡清醒啊\N渡,现在是清醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.34,0:09:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对\N令他从坏人中清醒过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡是坏孩子吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.38,0:09:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,现在的渡是坏孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡是坏孩子吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.95,0:09:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离死亡时间还有20秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.09,0:09:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有10秒\N8秒,7秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.43,0:09:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡…\N罗嗦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.76,0:09:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了什么来到这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.40,0:09:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有5秒\N渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想想创界山的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了坏事的时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有四秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这时候在下怎样也不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.41,0:10:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但求你现在记起\N正义的心一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3、2…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.52,0:10:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!\N喂,火美子,坏孩子快飞走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.33,0:10:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗?\N坏念头很快就会进入人心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.10,0:10:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候就想起老婆婆的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.21,0:10:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一定会变回好孩子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.78,0:10:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,那个方法啊\N好,渡,我来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.22,0:10:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏孩子快飞走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.00,0:11:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅,世伯!\N渡,你醒了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.70,0:11:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.80,0:11:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡。你终于清醒了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.63,0:11:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是在下的徒弟\N我的方法有效了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.54,0:11:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟被这幼稚的方法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.91,0:11:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时计虽然可以推进\N但却不可以停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.48,0:11:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非你通过了魔幻地狱门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.38,0:11:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的关系\N令时间减少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.96,0:12:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻婆婆婆,出口在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你通过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.53,0:12:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是明王哥哥\N我是明王弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.27,0:12:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集齐二人就无敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看哪处?\N这边啊,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.16,0:12:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.86,0:13:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们力量不及它,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.46,0:13:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.37,0:13:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成龙王丸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.40,0:13:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量全开!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变身!龙王丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.95,0:14:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你看看我们的厉害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.15,0:14:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金波士,金波士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.06,0:14:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙王丸,快跳起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让你成功吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.44,0:14:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎龙拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了,在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变形!凤凰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边!这边!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤雷炮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.34,0:15:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了,好,再来一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.21,0:15:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连续机关炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.28,0:15:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥,击倒他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.02,0:15:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.09,0:15:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.13,0:15:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题,龙王丸\N就这样子装成掉下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.10,0:15:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N要令他们大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.73,0:15:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,虽然危险,试试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.34,0:15:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续下去太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.64,0:15:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够,要再接近地面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去,掉下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.72,0:15:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,是时候了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.59,0:15:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变形!龙王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.82,0:15:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机会了!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.25,0:15:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.80,0:16:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.47,0:16:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤龙剑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第四条钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.38,0:16:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡\N那是魔幻地狱门出口的门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.72,0:17:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,快点啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.46,0:17:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是这些钥匙内\N其中一条…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.57,0:17:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来有这小手脚吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.64,0:17:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡很聪明呢\N是这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.74,0:17:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小渡…\N我现在立即开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.78,0:17:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.22,0:17:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转不动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.53,0:17:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有些形状啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.20,0:17:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,这个要对得准确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.84,0:17:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…北是上面\N东是哪一边呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.58,0:18:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到你弄完后我已死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.48,0:18:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,东是右边啊\N好,是这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.91,0:18:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!通过魔幻地狱门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你们有命离开吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.25,0:19:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.38,0:19:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.92,0:19:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还连着呢\N好重,快走开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.65,0:19:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…\N渡,火美子,做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.82,0:19:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算得上什么?\N我只是出了点力就是这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.47,0:19:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紫龙啊\N紫龙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.67,0:19:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个麻婆婆婆吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.20,0:19:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是多恶达的魔力\N令她变成那样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.85,0:19:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.82,0:19:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.56,0:19:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你去救出圣龙妃和翔龙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.66,0:19:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣龙妃和翔龙子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.46,0:19:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是创界山的女王和她的王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.87,0:20:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个创界山是由女王圣龙妃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.34,0:20:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从第七界层开始\N带给这里和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七色的彩虹就是证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.78,0:20:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是保护着女王的七色龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.98,0:20:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻化成的神部七龙神的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.72,0:20:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们二人现在\N被多恶达的魔神幽禁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.50,0:20:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一日不救出他们\N就不能令创界山恢复和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.00,0:20:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了\N我一定会打倒多恶达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.07,0:20:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们二人救出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.27,0:20:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你去找龙王之剑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.64,0:20:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙王之剑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.51,0:20:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是唯一能打倒多恶达的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那把剑在什么地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.95,0:20:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就在第七界层\N的某个地方才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个地方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.22,0:20:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能找出来的\N没有那把剑就打不倒多恶达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.56,0:20:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了\N总之我们上第七界层吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.73,0:21:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是\N通往第七界层的彩虹在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.96,0:21:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢…\N从刚才起我就开始找了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.17,0:21:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四处也没有呢\N喂!彩虹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有彩虹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.07,0:21:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…\N请看那边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.01,0:21:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第七界层的底部\N只能从那里上地面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.19,0:21:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七界层有一条白龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.99,0:21:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白龙手上的龙神之盾\N能压制多恶达的魔力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.30,0:21:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当龙神之盾和龙王之剑\N也得到手的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.07,0:21:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说的救世主就会成为真实\N也可令我们神部七龙神苏醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.81,0:21:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七界层现在是个\N很可怕的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.01,0:21:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预防万一,你拿这个去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.89,0:22:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.56,0:22:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,紫龙


